// Test: inlining-multiple-calls
function square(x int) returns int
    return x * x
end 'square'

function main() returns int
    return square(3) + square(4)
end 'main'
---
ExitCode: 25
RequiredMlir: ```
func.func @main() -> i64 {
  ^entry:
    x86.prologue stack_size=32
    x86.mov rax, 25
    x86.epilogue
    x86.ret
}
```
